1
00:00:10,656 --> 00:00:12,937
(Turn off the TV when sleeping.)

2
00:00:13,297 --> 00:00:14,577
(The blue light from the TV)

3
00:00:14,577 --> 00:00:16,177
(suppresses melatonin production.)

4
00:00:16,417 --> 00:00:17,696
(It affects sleep quality.)

5
00:00:18,136 --> 00:00:20,056
(Your cells think it's still daytime.)

6
00:00:28,217 --> 00:00:29,737
Just leave a floor lamp on.

7
00:00:29,937 --> 00:00:31,296
It's soft and comfortable.

8
00:00:36,656 --> 00:00:38,217
You set the AC so low again.

9
00:00:38,616 --> 00:00:40,416
Turn my back,
and you're rushing for the cold.

10
00:00:40,937 --> 00:00:43,497
Body temperature drops during sleep.

11
00:00:43,616 --> 00:00:44,736
Makes you prone to chills.

12
00:00:48,696 --> 00:00:50,096
Instant noodles again?

13
00:00:50,736 --> 00:00:52,217
At the business dinner earlier,

14
00:00:52,217 --> 00:00:54,056
the table was full of delicacies.

15
00:00:54,897 --> 00:00:56,217
If you didn't like them,

16
00:00:56,537 --> 00:00:58,696
I'll have them prepare
some vegetables for you

17
00:00:59,096 --> 00:01:00,857
or make some soup.

18
00:01:02,937 --> 00:01:04,416
I've always said

19
00:01:04,616 --> 00:01:05,457
that we

20
00:01:05,857 --> 00:01:07,296
should live in the sunlight,

21
00:01:08,056 --> 00:01:09,497
eat like humans,

22
00:01:09,736 --> 00:01:11,096
sleep like humans,

23
00:01:11,536 --> 00:01:12,896
and breathe like humans.

24
00:01:13,736 --> 00:01:15,656
We should live ordinary lives.

25
00:01:16,337 --> 00:01:17,937
Remember, jade towers and palaces

26
00:01:18,497 --> 00:01:19,857
are cold at their heights.

27
00:01:28,096 --> 00:01:28,896
Oh,

28
00:01:29,016 --> 00:01:30,337
my special hangover cure.

29
00:01:30,456 --> 00:01:31,896
I'll make it and set it by your bed.

30
00:01:32,096 --> 00:01:32,896
Ruoxi,

31
00:01:34,137 --> 00:01:34,937
don't go.

32
00:01:38,816 --> 00:01:39,857
If I leave,

33
00:01:41,016 --> 00:01:42,617
will you live peacefully?

34
00:01:47,256 --> 00:01:48,296
Tu Jiasheng,

35
00:01:49,137 --> 00:01:51,456
I don't want you
to live like a ghost anymore.

36
00:01:51,896 --> 00:01:53,137
You recognized me.

37
00:01:53,137 --> 00:01:54,736
Then explain it clearly!

38
00:01:55,417 --> 00:01:57,337
Stop using mental illness as an excuse.

39
00:01:57,417 --> 00:01:58,497
Tu Jiasheng!

40
00:01:58,497 --> 00:01:59,697
Wake up!

41
00:01:59,816 --> 00:02:01,137
Snap out of it!

42
00:02:03,256 --> 00:02:04,417
Jiasheng,

43
00:02:04,536 --> 00:02:05,896
I want to tell you.

44
00:02:06,337 --> 00:02:08,536
I will take back everything

45
00:02:08,656 --> 00:02:10,296
you possess now.

46
00:02:12,896 --> 00:02:15,136
My people are already moving.

47
00:02:15,457 --> 00:02:17,256
About that diary,

48
00:02:17,897 --> 00:02:19,136
you know what I mean.

49
00:02:23,904 --> 00:02:26,432
=The Glory Fades=

50
00:02:27,072 --> 00:02:29,344
=Episode 10=
(Yunyan's Dream)

51
00:03:52,696 --> 00:03:53,297
(Jiasheng,)

52
00:03:53,976 --> 00:03:55,072
(let me know when awake.)

53
00:03:55,416 --> 00:03:57,280
(I'll brief you
on the meeting with Mr. Tang.)

54
00:03:58,057 --> 00:03:58,976
(I'm awake.)

55
00:04:04,696 --> 00:04:05,497
What's wrong?

56
00:04:05,497 --> 00:04:06,297
Didn't sleep well?

57
00:04:08,897 --> 00:04:09,656
Lu,

58
00:04:10,617 --> 00:04:12,737
did you come back
after leaving last night?

59
00:04:13,177 --> 00:04:14,017
No.

60
00:04:18,376 --> 00:04:19,217
Honey water.

61
00:04:29,336 --> 00:04:30,136
How are you?

62
00:04:30,776 --> 00:04:31,937
Can you manage?

63
00:04:32,136 --> 00:04:34,016
I'm not some fragile paper doll.

64
00:04:34,336 --> 00:04:36,336
Staying up late and rising early?

65
00:04:36,737 --> 00:04:37,497
No problem.

66
00:04:38,417 --> 00:04:39,497
Still hiding it from me?

67
00:04:40,417 --> 00:04:42,016
You got slapped, no?

68
00:04:42,737 --> 00:04:43,617
Does it hurt?

69
00:04:45,177 --> 00:04:47,016
Good news never leaves the house,

70
00:04:47,016 --> 00:04:48,456
but bad news travels afar.

71
00:04:49,937 --> 00:04:51,097
Who told you?

72
00:04:51,816 --> 00:04:52,617
Who was it?

73
00:04:53,216 --> 00:04:54,576
Such a gossip!

74
00:04:59,576 --> 00:05:00,857
Do you really feel

75
00:05:01,177 --> 00:05:02,497
this place full of trivial love

76
00:05:02,776 --> 00:05:04,057
and betrayal is any fun?

77
00:05:06,297 --> 00:05:07,336
It's truly meaningless.

78
00:05:08,376 --> 00:05:09,297
Gives me a headache.

79
00:05:11,097 --> 00:05:11,896
So

80
00:05:13,376 --> 00:05:14,177
just quit.

81
00:05:15,216 --> 00:05:16,537
If you need money,

82
00:05:16,537 --> 00:05:17,896
I can find a way.

83
00:05:21,097 --> 00:05:23,297
I can't just be a waitress.

84
00:05:23,816 --> 00:05:25,417
I need to get close to those officials.

85
00:05:27,016 --> 00:05:27,857
Don't you agree?

86
00:05:30,097 --> 00:05:31,297
You're allergic to honey.

87
00:05:31,537 --> 00:05:33,376
Who'd dare leave honey water for you?

88
00:05:34,617 --> 00:05:36,657
Have you found Ruoxi's bracelet?

89
00:05:37,497 --> 00:05:38,057
You're worried

90
00:05:38,057 --> 00:05:39,737
someone used it to enter your room?

91
00:05:40,576 --> 00:05:41,896
If you're uneasy,

92
00:05:42,216 --> 00:05:44,097
I'll have the police check
internally again

93
00:05:44,097 --> 00:05:45,216
where that bracelet went.

94
00:05:47,937 --> 00:05:48,864
Hurry and get ready.

95
00:05:48,864 --> 00:05:49,737
We need to leave.

96
00:05:49,737 --> 00:05:50,977
Tang will wake up soon.

97
00:06:00,417 --> 00:06:01,216
Check it.

98
00:06:15,216 --> 00:06:17,497
You slept soundly until dawn.

99
00:06:17,977 --> 00:06:19,417
Your sleep quality has improved.

100
00:06:24,737 --> 00:06:26,216
In a few days, a master

101
00:06:26,376 --> 00:06:28,032
will check the feng shui
for our property.

102
00:06:28,816 --> 00:06:30,097
I think maybe we could

103
00:06:30,297 --> 00:06:31,937
have him perform a ritual for Ruoxi.

104
00:06:36,816 --> 00:06:37,857
Forget it.

105
00:06:38,136 --> 00:06:38,896
Let her

106
00:06:38,896 --> 00:06:40,776
return to dust and earth.

107
00:06:48,537 --> 00:06:49,177
Go ahead.

108
00:06:49,417 --> 00:06:50,216
Hello, Lu.

109
00:06:50,216 --> 00:06:51,297
We checked the camera.

110
00:06:51,297 --> 00:06:52,896
Someone did enter Mr. Tu's room.

111
00:06:53,216 --> 00:06:54,057
Hold on a second.

112
00:06:56,896 --> 00:06:57,537
Go ahead.

113
00:06:58,016 --> 00:06:58,937
It was Yunyan.

114
00:07:01,896 --> 00:07:03,177
Whose access card did she use?

115
00:07:03,576 --> 00:07:05,576
Yesterday, she hid
in the VIP room next door.

116
00:07:05,576 --> 00:07:07,177
As you entered, door left open,

117
00:07:07,177 --> 00:07:08,497
she slipped in secretly.

118
00:07:08,816 --> 00:07:09,776
I'm sorry, Lu.

119
00:07:09,776 --> 00:07:11,057
It was our fault.

120
00:07:11,336 --> 00:07:12,032
Enough talk.

121
00:07:12,032 --> 00:07:12,696
I'll be back.

122
00:07:16,696 --> 00:07:17,376
Turn around.

123
00:07:18,097 --> 00:07:18,896
Wait a minute.

124
00:07:19,497 --> 00:07:20,977
Tang's matter is quite important.

125
00:07:21,097 --> 00:07:22,376
Yunyan just wants to get ahead.

126
00:07:22,376 --> 00:07:23,456
She has no ill intentions.

127
00:07:23,776 --> 00:07:24,737
Let me handle this.

128
00:07:24,896 --> 00:07:25,977
I said turn around.

129
00:07:27,177 --> 00:07:28,016
Yes, Mr. Tu.

130
00:07:39,376 --> 00:07:40,297
Was it you?

131
00:07:41,497 --> 00:07:42,696
What's wrong?

132
00:07:45,896 --> 00:07:47,417
While Mr. Tu was asleep,

133
00:07:47,617 --> 00:07:48,776
you entered Room 999,

134
00:07:49,376 --> 00:07:51,537
turned off the TV,
turned on the floor lamp,

135
00:07:51,537 --> 00:07:52,576
adjusted the AC,

136
00:07:52,857 --> 00:07:53,896
and poured honey water,

137
00:07:55,216 --> 00:07:56,336
right?

138
00:07:59,376 --> 00:08:00,537
Ms. Bai,

139
00:08:01,376 --> 00:08:03,497
I really didn't do much.

140
00:08:03,497 --> 00:08:05,057
Just small things.

141
00:08:05,937 --> 00:08:07,576
What are you trying to do, Yunyan?

142
00:08:07,576 --> 00:08:09,297
Are you a newbie on your first day?

143
00:08:09,937 --> 00:08:11,776
How could you make such a basic mistake?

144
00:08:14,417 --> 00:08:15,857
Ms. Bai,

145
00:08:16,216 --> 00:08:18,016
I know the rules.

146
00:08:18,537 --> 00:08:20,857
I know no one is allowed

147
00:08:21,016 --> 00:08:23,617
to enter Room 999 without permission.

148
00:08:24,136 --> 00:08:26,376
But ever since Ruoxi left,

149
00:08:26,497 --> 00:08:28,376
Mr. Tu hasn't been happy.

150
00:08:28,537 --> 00:08:30,376
Everyone can see it.

151
00:08:31,177 --> 00:08:32,497
I know

152
00:08:32,617 --> 00:08:34,617
I'm not as charming as Ruoxi.

153
00:08:34,857 --> 00:08:37,177
I never thought about climbing
the social ladder.

154
00:08:38,216 --> 00:08:40,937
I just wanted to try my best

155
00:08:40,937 --> 00:08:42,177
to do some

156
00:08:42,417 --> 00:08:43,537
small things,

157
00:08:44,017 --> 00:08:46,297
so Mr. Tu could get a sound sleep.

158
00:08:47,816 --> 00:08:49,417
If you're putting it like that,

159
00:08:50,096 --> 00:08:51,616
I don't know what else to say.

160
00:08:53,137 --> 00:08:54,777
Let Mr. Tu and Mr. Zhao to handle it.

161
00:08:57,216 --> 00:08:58,017
Come in.

162
00:09:04,377 --> 00:09:05,177
Ms. Bai.

163
00:09:05,177 --> 00:09:06,377
What are you doing here?

164
00:09:06,777 --> 00:09:07,377
Get out.

165
00:09:07,377 --> 00:09:08,937
This is my office.

166
00:09:16,377 --> 00:09:17,096
By the way,

167
00:09:17,777 --> 00:09:18,897
last night I saw

168
00:09:18,897 --> 00:09:20,177
a red handprint on her face.

169
00:09:21,017 --> 00:09:22,017
Was that you?

170
00:09:22,616 --> 00:09:23,976
Yes, Ms. Bai.

171
00:09:24,576 --> 00:09:26,257
Yunyan slapped me.

172
00:09:26,336 --> 00:09:27,216
Reason?

173
00:09:30,336 --> 00:09:31,937
Ms. Bai,

174
00:09:32,336 --> 00:09:34,257
you see how arrogant she is.

175
00:09:34,377 --> 00:09:35,456
Relying on the fact

176
00:09:35,456 --> 00:09:37,216
she looks somewhat like An Ruoxi,

177
00:09:37,297 --> 00:09:38,736
she throws her weight around

178
00:09:38,736 --> 00:09:39,897
at Deep In The Bustle.

179
00:09:39,897 --> 00:09:42,456
I was teaching her
a lesson on your behalf.

180
00:09:42,736 --> 00:09:44,057
On my behalf?

181
00:09:44,816 --> 00:09:46,336
I think you're burning with jealousy

182
00:09:46,336 --> 00:09:47,816
because she resembles An Ruoxi.

183
00:09:48,816 --> 00:09:51,137
When will you ever use your head?

184
00:09:59,137 --> 00:10:00,057
What's the matter?

185
00:10:00,816 --> 00:10:01,736
Ms. Bai,

186
00:10:02,057 --> 00:10:03,377
may I transfer

187
00:10:03,897 --> 00:10:04,897
to a different position?

188
00:10:05,177 --> 00:10:06,897
Stop pretending to be pure.

189
00:10:07,216 --> 00:10:08,992
I think you're just jealous

190
00:10:08,992 --> 00:10:09,816
that we earn more.

191
00:10:09,816 --> 00:10:11,696
Because of your pretentiousness,

192
00:10:11,777 --> 00:10:13,216
my client left

193
00:10:13,336 --> 00:10:15,177
and He Cong lost his life!

194
00:10:15,177 --> 00:10:15,976
Yunyan!

195
00:10:17,177 --> 00:10:19,096
Do you have any sense of propriety left?

196
00:10:19,296 --> 00:10:19,816
(GM's Office)

197
00:10:19,816 --> 00:10:21,537
Ms. Bai!

198
00:10:22,017 --> 00:10:23,177
What evidence do you have

199
00:10:23,177 --> 00:10:24,496
that proves He Cong's death

200
00:10:24,496 --> 00:10:25,976
is related to Su Yunian?

201
00:10:26,897 --> 00:10:28,496
It was a traffic accident.

202
00:10:29,137 --> 00:10:31,177
What does it have to do
with Deep In The Bustle?

203
00:10:38,816 --> 00:10:39,777
Anything else?

204
00:10:40,496 --> 00:10:41,297
I...

205
00:10:48,856 --> 00:10:49,377
Hello?

206
00:10:49,576 --> 00:10:50,336
Mr. Zhao.

207
00:10:50,537 --> 00:10:51,177
Ms. Bai,

208
00:10:52,496 --> 00:10:53,937
pull Yunyan off stage.

209
00:10:56,616 --> 00:10:57,736
For how long?

210
00:10:58,017 --> 00:10:59,336
Mr. Tu will tell you himself.

211
00:11:05,616 --> 00:11:06,257
Hello.

212
00:11:06,456 --> 00:11:07,696
Put Yunyan on the phone.

213
00:11:09,216 --> 00:11:09,856
It's Mr. Tu.

214
00:11:18,777 --> 00:11:19,576
Hello,

215
00:11:20,417 --> 00:11:21,297
Mr. Tu.

216
00:11:22,257 --> 00:11:24,336
You want to take Ruoxi's position?

217
00:11:25,216 --> 00:11:26,137
You can have it.

218
00:11:46,576 --> 00:11:47,377
Jiasheng,

219
00:11:47,777 --> 00:11:49,096
Yunyan

220
00:11:49,096 --> 00:11:50,736
is our veteran

221
00:11:51,377 --> 00:11:52,576
and Ruoxi's best friend.

222
00:11:53,696 --> 00:11:54,657
How about

223
00:11:55,336 --> 00:11:56,657
leaving this to me?

224
00:11:56,937 --> 00:11:58,657
I'll set her straight.
You'll be satisfied.

225
00:11:59,377 --> 00:12:00,177
What do you say?

226
00:12:03,576 --> 00:12:05,216
I'll handle this personally.

227
00:12:05,937 --> 00:12:06,976
Stick to our plan.

228
00:12:06,976 --> 00:12:08,456
Accompany Tang to see that land.

229
00:12:09,096 --> 00:12:10,057
Someone should be there.

230
00:12:11,576 --> 00:12:12,377
Mr. Tu.

231
00:12:17,216 --> 00:12:18,017
Mr. Tu.

232
00:12:20,216 --> 00:12:20,897
Mr. Zhao.

233
00:12:28,976 --> 00:12:30,297
Did you touch the files?

234
00:12:37,377 --> 00:12:38,417
Mr. Tu,

235
00:12:38,897 --> 00:12:41,017
I know I broke the rules,

236
00:12:41,336 --> 00:12:42,937
but I meant no harm.

237
00:12:43,576 --> 00:12:45,777
I saw when you were asleep,

238
00:12:46,017 --> 00:12:47,537
the TV was still on.

239
00:12:48,096 --> 00:12:49,537
I worried it might disturb you,

240
00:12:49,537 --> 00:12:50,037
so

241
00:12:50,057 --> 00:12:51,417
I turned it off.

242
00:12:57,177 --> 00:12:57,976
I'm asking you.

243
00:13:07,216 --> 00:13:08,816
Did you touch the files?

244
00:13:09,777 --> 00:13:10,496
Mr. Tu,

245
00:13:10,777 --> 00:13:11,696
I wanted...

246
00:13:11,856 --> 00:13:13,417
- I just wanted...
- Wanted what?

247
00:13:14,976 --> 00:13:16,576
I just missed Ruoxi.

248
00:13:16,897 --> 00:13:18,297
I wanted to see her photo

249
00:13:18,297 --> 00:13:19,576
and talked to her.

250
00:13:40,736 --> 00:13:42,017
For your family.

251
00:13:42,137 --> 00:13:43,137
A small token.

252
00:13:48,377 --> 00:13:49,736
Thank you, Mr. Tu.

253
00:13:50,297 --> 00:13:51,377
Mr. Tu,

254
00:13:51,616 --> 00:13:53,017
I only did

255
00:13:53,017 --> 00:13:54,616
a small favor casually.

256
00:13:54,736 --> 00:13:56,177
No need for gifts.

257
00:13:56,177 --> 00:13:57,216
You've been here for long.

258
00:13:57,377 --> 00:13:58,616
A reward is deserved.

259
00:14:00,976 --> 00:14:01,576
Manni,

260
00:14:02,496 --> 00:14:03,937
give Yunyan the afternoon off

261
00:14:04,417 --> 00:14:05,377
to take the money home

262
00:14:06,017 --> 00:14:07,552
or deposit it and bring the card back.

263
00:14:08,937 --> 00:14:10,297
Yes, Mr. Tu.

264
00:14:10,937 --> 00:14:11,496
Mr. Tu.

265
00:14:11,496 --> 00:14:12,216
Also,

266
00:14:12,976 --> 00:14:13,937
take the driver,

267
00:14:14,496 --> 00:14:15,696
find her parents

268
00:14:16,216 --> 00:14:17,177
and give them gifts.

269
00:14:18,017 --> 00:14:18,816
Handle anything else

270
00:14:19,137 --> 00:14:20,096
as you see fit.

271
00:14:22,216 --> 00:14:22,897
Okay.

272
00:14:23,696 --> 00:14:24,616
Understood.

273
00:14:26,777 --> 00:14:28,096
Thank you, Mr. Tu.

274
00:14:41,576 --> 00:14:42,377
Ms. Bai,

275
00:14:42,897 --> 00:14:44,576
thank you so much

276
00:14:44,696 --> 00:14:46,216
for helping me all afternoon.

277
00:14:46,816 --> 00:14:47,616
Yunyan,

278
00:14:49,017 --> 00:14:50,897
you've wanted this
all along, haven't you?

279
00:14:52,657 --> 00:14:53,456
Ms. Bai.

280
00:14:53,456 --> 00:14:54,696
Tell me the truth.

281
00:14:58,937 --> 00:15:00,576
To be honest,

282
00:15:01,417 --> 00:15:02,976
Ruoxi and I

283
00:15:03,336 --> 00:15:04,816
were best friends after all.

284
00:15:05,377 --> 00:15:07,496
My feelings for her were genuine.

285
00:15:08,897 --> 00:15:10,096
I just want you to know.

286
00:15:11,177 --> 00:15:13,216
Life is constant choices.

287
00:15:13,576 --> 00:15:14,736
You made the choice,

288
00:15:14,976 --> 00:15:15,897
so don't regret it.

289
00:15:16,576 --> 00:15:17,377
Ms. Bai,

290
00:15:17,616 --> 00:15:18,537
I have no regrets.

291
00:15:23,096 --> 00:15:24,257
Good that you don't.

292
00:15:27,177 --> 00:15:28,177
Rest assured.

293
00:15:28,177 --> 00:15:30,057
If I ever make it big,

294
00:15:30,257 --> 00:15:31,576
I won't forget you.

295
00:16:09,216 --> 00:16:10,736
(Let me tell you again.)

296
00:16:11,496 --> 00:16:13,456
(Hand it over now.)

297
00:16:14,096 --> 00:16:15,417
(Don't try tricks.)

298
00:16:16,057 --> 00:16:17,096
It won't help.

299
00:16:24,696 --> 00:16:25,696
Tu Jiasheng,

300
00:16:25,696 --> 00:16:26,937
you got skills.

301
00:16:27,057 --> 00:16:29,216
(You'd better hide it well.)

302
00:16:33,216 --> 00:16:34,856
(If I find out,)

303
00:16:35,257 --> 00:16:37,456
(I'll make you pay!)

304
00:16:48,057 --> 00:16:49,257
Jiasheng,

305
00:16:49,496 --> 00:16:51,496
I've been too nice to you!

306
00:17:11,872 --> 00:17:15,546
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

307
00:17:15,845 --> 00:17:19,036
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

308
00:17:20,868 --> 00:17:24,489
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

309
00:17:25,038 --> 00:17:27,968
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

310
00:17:29,308 --> 00:17:33,038
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

311
00:17:33,262 --> 00:17:36,759
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

312
00:17:38,158 --> 00:17:41,845
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

313
00:17:42,483 --> 00:17:47,598
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

314
00:17:48,302 --> 00:17:52,436
♪I feel guilty♪

315
00:17:53,006 --> 00:17:56,750
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

316
00:17:57,614 --> 00:18:01,057
♪Even in tears♪

317
00:18:01,806 --> 00:18:05,720
♪It doesn't matter♪

318
00:18:05,902 --> 00:18:09,725
♪We embrace in dreams♪

319
00:18:10,574 --> 00:18:14,012
♪I let down all my defenses♪

320
00:18:15,246 --> 00:18:18,609
♪Though the story has its end♪

321
00:18:19,374 --> 00:18:26,880
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
